{"nodes": [{"id": "claude_medgram_blueprint", "label": "Blueprint Plataforma de Marketing M\u00e9dico para Instagram", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a71 Objetivo", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_doctor_approval_gate", "label": "Gate de Aprobaci\u00f3n Obligatorio del Doctor", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72, \u00a76", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "La automatizaci\u00f3n 100% sin supervisi\u00f3n es mala idea para contenido m\u00e9dico: hay marco regulatorio real (Colegio M\u00e9dico, Ley 20.584, pol\u00edticas de salud de Meta). Consecuencia de dise\u00f1o: las restricciones son reglas duras del pipeline y el dashboard muestra un checklist de compliance visible junto a cada pieza, no solo el contenido."}, {"id": "claude_meta_personal_attributes_policy", "label": "Meta Personal Attributes Policy", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_meta_health_ads_policy", "label": "Meta Health & Wellness Ads Policy (2026)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Proh\u00edbe lenguaje diagn\u00f3stico, claims sin respaldo y antes/despu\u00e9s incluyendo transformaciones impl\u00edcitas (ampliaci\u00f3n 2026); cuentas de salud reciben escrutinio m\u00e1s agresivo y rechazos/restricciones son comunes."}, {"id": "claude_colegio_medico_codigo_etica", "label": "Colegio M\u00e9dico de Chile \u2014 C\u00f3digo de \u00c9tica", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_ley_20584", "label": "Ley 20.584 (Chile) \u2014 Derechos y Deberes de los Pacientes", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_content_pipeline", "label": "Generador IA de Contenido (copy, imagen, guion video)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a73, \u00a74", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Video/reels es lo m\u00e1s limitado hoy: evaluar guion+storyboard IA con edici\u00f3n humana vs proveedor de video-IA externo; no hay soluci\u00f3n 'un clic' confiable para reels m\u00e9dicos."}, {"id": "claude_compliance_check", "label": "Chequeo Autom\u00e1tico de Compliance", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a76", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Si un borrador falla el chequeo no llega al doctor, vuelve a generaci\u00f3n. El chequeo reduce el riesgo, no lo elimina: el doctor sigue siendo responsable legal del contenido publicado en su nombre."}, {"id": "claude_approval_dashboard", "label": "Dashboard de Aprobaci\u00f3n del Doctor", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a73, \u00a76", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Una sola pantalla: preview real del post/reel, texto y checklist de compliance resuelto (verde/rojo por regla). Acciones: Aprobar, Rechazar con motivo, Pedir cambios."}, {"id": "claude_publish_scheduler", "label": "Programador de Publicaci\u00f3n", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a73", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Rate limits de Meta se basan en la f\u00f3rmula Business Use Case, no un l\u00edmite fijo: hay que dejar margen en el dise\u00f1o de la cola (BullMQ + Redis para reintentos)."}, {"id": "claude_instagram_graph_api", "label": "Instagram Graph API (Content Publishing)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a77", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Requiere cuenta IG Business vinculada a P\u00e1gina de Facebook y Meta App Review (~2-4 semanas) para permisos instagram_business_basic/instagram_business_content_publish. Modelo: crear container, esperar procesamiento, publicar."}, {"id": "claude_meta_marketing_api", "label": "Meta Marketing API (Ads)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a78", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Se construye al final, no en el MVP: es donde m\u00e1s plata y reputaci\u00f3n se puede perder por un rechazo o restricci\u00f3n de cuenta; anuncios de salud reciben categorizaci\u00f3n especial y escrutinio m\u00e1s agresivo."}, {"id": "claude_contentitem", "label": "ContentItem (modelo de datos)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "M\u00e1quina de estados central: draft -> pending_approval -> (approved | rejected | needs_changes) -> scheduled -> published."}, {"id": "claude_compliancecheck_model", "label": "ComplianceCheck (modelo de datos)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_campaign", "label": "Campaign (modelo de datos, fase 3)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_user", "label": "User (modelo de datos: agency_admin | doctor_approver)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_tech_stack", "label": "Stack Recomendado (Next.js, NestJS, PostgreSQL, BullMQ+Redis)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a74", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "claude_phased_rollout", "label": "Fases 1-3 de Construcci\u00f3n", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a79", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Fase 1 (generaci\u00f3n + aprobaci\u00f3n + publicaci\u00f3n manual) da algo usable y vendible en d\u00edas y separa 'el doctor aprueba contenido' (coraz\u00f3n de la propuesta de valor) de 'la API de Meta coopera' (fuera de control propio). Fase 2 requiere Meta App Review; Fase 3 (ads) es el mayor riesgo."}, {"id": "claude_audit_log", "label": "Log Inmutable de Auditor\u00eda de Aprobaciones", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a711", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Guardar qui\u00e9n aprob\u00f3 qu\u00e9 y cu\u00e1ndo: importante si algo se cuestiona despu\u00e9s, porque el doctor es el responsable legal del contenido publicado a su nombre."}, {"id": "claude_third_party_publishing", "label": "Capas Unificadas de Terceros (Blotato, Zernio, Postproxy)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a77 Atajo de MVP", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Evitan el ciclo de Meta App Review para publicar m\u00e1s r\u00e1pido. Trade-off: dependencia de un tercero, costo recurrente y due diligence de sus t\u00e9rminos de manejo de datos antes de conectarlos a la cuenta de un m\u00e9dico."}], "edges": [{"source": "claude_meta_personal_attributes_policy", "target": "claude_doctor_approval_gate", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_meta_health_ads_policy", "target": "claude_doctor_approval_gate", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_colegio_medico_codigo_etica", "target": "claude_doctor_approval_gate", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_ley_20584", "target": "claude_doctor_approval_gate", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_content_pipeline", "target": "claude_compliance_check", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a76.1", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_content_pipeline", "target": "claude_approval_dashboard", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a73 diagrama (cola pending_approval)", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_approval_dashboard", "target": "claude_publish_scheduler", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a73 diagrama", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_publish_scheduler", "target": "claude_instagram_graph_api", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": "\u00a73 diagrama", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "claude_meta_marketing_api", "target": "claude_doctor_approval_gate", "relation": "reference